    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在处理输入来源这块，我列出三种情况：管道输入用 cat my_file.txt | sed do_something，直接读文件用 sed do_something my_file.txt，还有原地修改用 sed --in-place do_something my_file.txt。这样覆盖全吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
